{"tid":161382,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【又有勵志故事】90後買Monterey：大學畢業開始儲錢","createTime":"2017-03-18T13:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T12:32:55.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7e55f60b5693aaa9b5382ebd169e878bd873db39","tid":161382,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T13:33:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/18/213250_35d7f59b7b544d2cf48b1475471ce35f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F18%2F213250_35d7f59b7b544d2cf48b1475471ce35f.jpg&h=66441968&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大學畢業起開始儲錢買錢，家陣已經買到。<br />\n<br />\n現時27歲的90後陳先生，是首次置業人士，今日揀咗將軍澳Monterey一間2房單位，樓價約700萬元，未決定入伙後會用作自住抑或投資，但相信區內物業有升值潛力，打算承造六成按揭，首期部份由家人資助，而自己由大學畢業起已經開始儲<br />\n<br />\n蓄。對於美國往後加息，本港樓揭息口有機會隨之調升，陳先生指置業前有計過數。<br />\n<br />\n掌握財經生活資訊，即Like「蘋果ATM」fb專頁啦！<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/appledailyatm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fappledailyatm&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHX0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=17ab11a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/appledailyatm</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56447201&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170318\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56447201%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170318&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHX0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=2fb5ab7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56447201%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170318&h=be395ce0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56447201&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170318</a>"},{"pid":"83e51d032c5313587e47c00e2ad4c853b383fdc6","tid":161382,"uid":67195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"